WEBVTT

00:00:01.330 --> 00:00:04.969
So, if there's no other comments, it looks like we're all in agreement.

00:00:04.969 --> 00:00:09.330
Mario will take over Fort Thomas at the Field Service Group over here.

00:00:09.330 --> 00:00:11.130
And I think that's the last item.

00:00:11.130 --> 00:00:15.320
So maybe Brother Leon, could you offer the closing prayer?

00:00:15.320 --> 00:00:20.000
Or Father Jehovah.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.210
Mario? Seriously?

00:00:24.210 --> 00:00:28.050
He's practically a kid.

00:00:28.050 --> 00:00:38.350
He's barely been serving a year.

00:00:38.350 --> 00:00:43.369
Sure. He gives a good talk.

00:00:43.369 --> 00:00:47.609
But he's not ready for this kind of responsibility.

00:00:47.729 --> 00:00:53.420
That's an assignment I definitely have the experience for.

00:00:53.420 --> 00:00:58.020
And now I'm stuck being his assistant.

00:00:58.020 --> 00:01:13.670
This is going to be a mess.

00:01:13.670 --> 00:01:16.069
Still disappointed?

00:01:16.069 --> 00:01:18.629
Just doesn't make sense.

00:01:18.629 --> 00:01:24.189
If it makes you feel any better, I think you'd have done great in that assignment.

00:01:24.189 --> 00:01:26.189
Thanks.

00:01:26.189 --> 00:01:29.829
But give Mario a chance.

00:01:29.829 --> 00:01:36.319
Okay. I will.

00:01:36.319 --> 00:01:52.549
With time, I saw exactly why Mario was being used like this.

00:01:52.549 --> 00:02:26.919
I just had to be patient and check my ego so I could see what Jehovah sees.

00:02:26.919 --> 00:02:30.319
And appreciate the privileges I do have.
